{"hash":"c1aaf37356b5601d03c49a9f63a0a08092cf0e97","data":{"markdownPage":{"id":"faecab0dc505435fcbf3dec671c5a1d1","title":"Desktop Application","description":"","path":"/docs/desktop-application/","timeToRead":1,"content":"<h2 id=\"desktop-application\"><a href=\"#desktop-application\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Desktop Application</h2>\n<p>This is the GUI application. It's built using <a href=\"https://wails.app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">wails</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\"><a href=\"#prerequisites\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Prerequisites</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Go 1.12+</li>\n<li>npm</li>\n<li>net5 SDK (Optional, only required if you're using the monitor)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"linux\"><a href=\"#linux\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Linux</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>gcc, gtk, webkitgtk</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"running-locally\"><a href=\"#running-locally\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Running locally</h2>\n<h3 id=\"flowcontrol\"><a href=\"#flowcontrol\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>flowcontrol</h3>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd src/flowcontrol/\nwails serve\n\ncd src/flowcontrol/frontend\nnpm run serve</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"flowcontrol-monitor\"><a href=\"#flowcontrol-monitor\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>flowcontrol-monitor</h3>\n<p>This is the supplementary application to the main one. It provides system metrics such as GPU Clock and temperatures using <a href=\"https://github.com/LibreHardwareMonitor/LibreHardwareMonitor\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">LibreHardwareMonitorLib</a>. I'm aiming to make this an optional component for people who want hardware metrics beyond the scope of the controller, it's currently bundled with the release.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">cd src/flowcontrol-monitor/\ndotnet run</code></pre>\n","sidebar":"docs","next":"","prev":"","headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Desktop Application","anchor":"#desktop-application"},{"depth":2,"value":"Prerequisites","anchor":"#prerequisites"},{"depth":3,"value":"Linux","anchor":"#linux"},{"depth":2,"value":"Running locally","anchor":"#running-locally"},{"depth":3,"value":"flowcontrol","anchor":"#flowcontrol"},{"depth":3,"value":"flowcontrol-monitor","anchor":"#flowcontrol-monitor"}]},"allMarkdownPage":{"edges":[{"node":{"path":"/docs/pcb/","title":"PCB"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/local-development/","title":"Local Development"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/","title":"Introduction"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/firmware/","title":"Firmware"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/documentation/","title":"Documentation"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/desktop-application/","title":"Desktop Application"}},{"node":{"path":"/docs/cli/","title":"CLI"}}]}},"context":{}}